#id=1
#text=I decided to bake a cake the other day .
#id=2
#text=I took a look around my kitchen and I had everything I needed , so I did n't need to go to the store .
#id=3
#text=I pulled up a recipe on my tablet and started collecting all the ingredients .
#id=4
#text=Once I had everything on the counter , I looked at what measures I would need and got out the cups and teaspoons and all the bowls I 'd need to mix it in .
#id=5
#text=I started by measuring out the dry ingredients like flour and sugar and put them in the bowl .
#id=6
#text=Then I added things like the eggs and milk and mixed it all up using my electric mixer .
#id=7
#text=About halfway through I turned the oven on to preheat .
#id=8
#text=I finished mixing everything and got it into the cake pan .
#id=9
#text=I set a timer and stated putting the dirty dished in the sink to wash .
#text=I decided that they would keep for a little while and waited until later that night .
#text=When the cake was done I let it cool off and put chocolate frosting on it .
#text=Everyone agreed it was a really good cake , and washing the dishes was n't that hard .
#text=I think I 'll bake a little more often .
